<center><h2>The Fishbowl Blog</h2></center>Do not be lulled into thinking that <b>The Fishbowl Network</b> is about fishes or bowls. As Wikipedia succinctly puts it, "A fishbowl conversation is a form of dialog that can be used when discussing topics within large groups". We represent exactly that ideal. A launchpad for talent, we nurture and let it flourish! We are an exuberant group of individuals, all but with one aim - to excel in our passions. Brace yourself - for a dashing experience awaits...
The Fishbowl Network. Fun. Excitement. Infotainment. It's all part of the package.
